org.hardroid.common

Class HumanActivity

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hardroid.common.HumanActivity
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.os.Parcelable

    public class HumanActivity
extends java.lang.Object
implements android.os.Parcelable
    A data class representing a Human Activity. A human activity consist of a type and a confidence level. All activities generated by ActivityRecognitionManager are guaranteed to have a valid type and confidence.
